tsdb.util.gui

Class ImageRGBA

  • java.lang.Object
    • tsdb.util.gui.ImageRGBA
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PureImage

    public class ImageRGBA
extends java.lang.Object
implements PureImage
    Base class of image creators. Image data is as an int array with one int per pixel and RGBA-Format (red, green, blue, alpha).
